    WA --> PRE
    SCHED --> ORCH
    TG --> PRE
    PRE --> ORCH
    ORCH --> HLIM
    HLIM --> SUP
    SUP --> SR
    SR --> SE
    SE --> CP
    CP --> COMP
    SR --> TC
    COMP --> OUT

    L0 -.-> ORCH
    L1 -.-> ORCH
    OI -.-> ORCH

    PII -.-> PLOG
    PII -.-> LF
    PLOG --> COST
    SR -.->|traced_node| LF

    SCHED --> ATTR
    SCHED --> D39
    SCHED --> IMPACT
    PAY --> ATTR
    D39 --> SHELLS
    D39 -.->|refund branch| REF

    STATE -.-> ORCH
    AUDIT -.-> PII
    DPA -.-> NOTICE
    SUP --> DBOS
    PLOG --> PG
    ATTR --> PG

    classDef done fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef inflight fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a8a,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef backlog fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:1.5px
